  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomised, controlled, double-blinded clinical study investigates the safety and
      efficacy of MBD in combination with PZQ in the treatment of SCH and STH in children aged 1-15
      years of age.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
